Interface StatisticCollector

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleStatisticCollector
    public interface StatisticCollector
extends java.lang.Runnable
    Base interface of Statistic collector. Provides method for collecting StatisticResult objects from test/html files The interface extends Runnable interface that allows to StatisticManager instance to run collecting process in separated thread Method returns StatisticResult object
